&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;gt;If HelloRetryRequest (HRR) is not required, the server should respond with ServerHello + ChangeCipherSpec&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;gt;If HRR is required, the server should respond with HRR + ChangeCipherSpec&lt;br/&gt;
